<lb ed="D" n="0779b01"/>孫賔門下因什麼鑽龜　僧拂袖出去　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云將為當
<lb ed="D" n="0779b02"/>榮折他雙足　<g ref="#CB28906"/><g ref="#CB10191"/>首座看石槗乃問首座是什麼人造
<lb ed="D" n="0779b03"/>云李膺造　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云造時向什麼<g ref="#CB20060"/>下手　無對　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云<g ref="#CB31905"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0779b04"/>常<g ref="#CB22072"/>石槗問<g ref="#CB29918"/>下手<g ref="#CB20060"/>也不知　有新羅院主請<g ref="#CB28906"/>齋
<lb ed="D" n="0779b05"/><g ref="#CB28906"/>到門首問此是什麼院　云新羅院　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云我与<g ref="#CB08859"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0779b06"/>隔海　問僧什麼<g ref="#CB20060"/>来　云雲居来　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云雲居有
<lb ed="D" n="0779b07"/>什麼言句　云有僧問靈羊掛角時如何　雲居云六
<lb ed="D" n="0779b08"/>六三十六　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云雲居<g ref="#CB28906"/>兄由在　僧却問未<g ref="#CB29823"/>和尚尊
<lb ed="D" n="0779b09"/>意如何　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云九九八十一　有一婆子日晚入院来　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云
<lb ed="D" n="0779b10"/>作什麼　婆云<g ref="#CB31257"/>宿　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云者裏是什麼所在　婆
<lb ed="D" n="0779b11"/>呵呵大<g ref="#CB20158"/>而去　<g ref="#CB28906"/>出外逢見一个婆子提一个籃子
<lb ed="D" n="0779b12"/><g ref="#CB28906"/>便問什麼<g ref="#CB20060"/>去　云偷趙州笋去　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云忽見趙州
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D48.8939.0780a" n="0780a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0780a01"/>又作麼生　婆子近前打一掌　<g ref="#CB28906"/>因見院主送生飯
<lb ed="D" n="0780a02"/>鵶子見便<g ref="#CB30106"/>飛去　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云鵶子見<g ref="#CB08859"/>為什麼却飛去
<lb ed="D" n="0780a03"/>院主云怕<g ref="#CB24959"/>甲　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云是什麼語話　<g ref="#CB28906"/>代云為厶甲有殺
<lb ed="D" n="0780a04"/>心在　<g ref="#CB28906"/>問僧什麼<g ref="#CB20060"/>来　云江西来　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云趙州<g ref="#CB29918"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0780a05"/>在什麼<g ref="#CB20060"/>　僧無對　<g ref="#CB28906"/><g ref="#CB28265"/>殿上過見一僧礼拜<g ref="#CB28906"/>打
<lb ed="D" n="0780a06"/>一棒　云礼拜也是好事　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云好事不如無　<g ref="#CB28906"/>因
<lb ed="D" n="0780a07"/>叅潼関潼関問<g ref="#CB28906"/>云<g ref="#CB08859"/>還知有潼関麼　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云知有
<lb ed="D" n="0780a08"/>潼関云有公驗者即得過無公驗者不得過　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云忽遇
<lb ed="D" n="0780a09"/>鑾駕來時如何　関云也湏檢點過　云<g ref="#CB08859"/>要造返。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0780a10"/><p xml:id="pD48p0780a1001"><g ref="#CB28906"/>到<g ref="#CB30988"/>壽<g ref="#CB30988"/>壽見<g ref="#CB28906"/>來遂乃背面而坐　<g ref="#CB28906"/>便展坐具
<lb ed="D" n="0780a11"/><g ref="#CB30988"/>壽起立　<g ref="#CB28906"/>便出去　<g ref="#CB28906"/>在南泉時泉牽一頭水牯牛
<lb ed="D" n="0780a12"/>入僧堂內巡堂而轉首座乃向牛背上三拍泉便休去<g ref="#CB28906"/>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D48.8939.0780b" n="0780b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0780b01"/>後將一束草安首座面前　首座無對　有秀才見
<lb ed="D" n="0780b02"/><g ref="#CB28906"/>乃讃嘆<g ref="#CB28906"/>云和尚是古佛　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云秀才是新如来
<lb ed="D" n="0780b03"/>有僧問如何是<g ref="#CB29810"/>槃　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云我耳重　僧再問　<g ref="#CB28906"/>云
<lb ed="D" n="0780b04"/>我不害耳聾乃有頌　滕滕大道者對面<g ref="#CB29810"/>槃門但
<lb ed="D" n="0780b05"/>坐念無際来年春又春　有僧問生死二路是同是別
<lb ed="D" n="0780b06"/>師乃有頌　道人問生死生死<g ref="#CB30132"/>為論雙林一池水朗月
<lb ed="D" n="0780b07"/>耀<g ref="#CB00371"/>坤喚他句上識此是弄精魂欲會个生死顛人<g ref="#CB22072"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0780b08"/>夢春　有僧問諸佛有難火焰裏蔵身和尚有難
<lb ed="D" n="0780b09"/>向什麼<g ref="#CB20060"/>蔵身　<g ref="#CB28906"/>乃有頌　渠<g ref="#CB22072"/>佛有難我<g ref="#CB22072"/>渠
<lb ed="D" n="0780b10"/>有灾但看我避難何<g ref="#CB20060"/>有相随有無不是<g ref="#CB22072"/>去來非
<lb ed="D" n="0780b11"/>去來為<g ref="#CB08859"/><g ref="#CB22072"/>難法對面識得未。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0780b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">偈頌</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">見起<g ref="#CB30259"/>乃有頌</cb:mulu><head>見起<g ref="#CB30259"/>乃有頌</head>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D48.8939.0781a" n="0781a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0781a01"/><lg xml:id="lgD48p0781a0101" type="abnormal" style="text-indent:0em"><l>本自圎成何勞疊石名邈雕鐫与吾懸隔<g ref="#CB30132"/>人借問
<lb ed="D" n="0781a02"/>終不<g ref="#CB31158"/>畫</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0781a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">因見諸方見解異途乃有頌呵</cb:mulu><head>因見諸方見解異途乃有頌呵</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0781a04"/><lg xml:id="lgD48p0781a0401" type="abnormal" style="text-indent:0em"><l>趙州南石槗北觀音院裏有<g ref="#CB12752"/>勒祖<g ref="#CB28906"/>遺下一隻履直
<lb ed="D" n="0781a05"/>至如今覔不得</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0781a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">因魚鼓有頌</cb:mulu><head>因魚鼓有頌</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0781a07"/><lg xml:id="lgD48p0781a0701" type="abnormal" style="text-indent:0em"><l>四大猶来造化功有声全貴裏頭空莫恠不与凡夫<g ref="#CB22072"/>只
<lb ed="D" n="0781a08"/>為宮<note n="0781a0801" resp="CBETA" type="add">商【CB】，啇【國圖】</note><app n="0781a0801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">商</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">啇</rdg></app>調不同</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0781a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">因蓮花有頌</cb:mulu><head>因蓮花有頌</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0781a10"/><lg xml:id="lgD48p0781a1001" type="abnormal" style="text-indent:0em"><l>竒異根苗帶雪鮮不知何代別西天淤泥深淺人不識
<lb ed="D" n="0781a11"/>出水方知是白蓮</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0781a12"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="6"><cb:jhead>趙州和尚下錄終</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D48.8939.0781b" n="0781b"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0781b01"/><cb:div type="w"><cb:mulu type="附文" level="3">趙王<g ref="#CB10191"/><g ref="#CB28906"/>作真讃</cb:mulu><head>趙王<g ref="#CB10191"/><g ref="#CB28906"/>作真讃</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0781b02"/><lg xml:id="lgD48p0781b0201" type="abnormal"><l style="text-indent:1em">碧溪之月</l><l style="text-indent:1em">清鏡中頭</l><l style="text-indent:1em">我<g ref="#CB28906"/>我化</l><l style="text-indent:1em">天下趙州</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0781b03"/><cb:div type="w"><cb:mulu type="附文" level="3">哭趙州和尚二首</cb:mulu><head>哭趙州和尚二首</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0781b04"/><cb:div type="w"><cb:mulu type="附文" level="4">其一</cb:mulu><lg xml:id="lgD48p0781b0401" type="abnormal" style="text-indent:0em"><l><g ref="#CB28906"/>離<g ref="#CB16341"/>水動王<g ref="#CB02523"/>心印光潜麈尾収碧落霧霾松嶺月
<lb ed="D" n="0781b05"/>滄溟浪覆濟人舟一燈乍<g ref="#CB29919"/>波旬喜雙眼重昏道侣愁
<lb ed="D" n="0781b06"/><g ref="#CB29793"/>是了然雲外客每瞻瓶机淚還流</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0781b07"/><cb:div type="w"><cb:mulu type="附文" level="4">其二</cb:mulu><head>其二</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0781b08"/><lg xml:id="lgD48p0781b0801" type="abnormal" style="text-indent:0em"><l>佛日<note n="0781b0801" resp="CBETA" type="add">西【CB】，覀【國圖】</note><app n="0781b0801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">西</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">覀</rdg></app>傾祖印隳珠沉円沼月沉輝影敷丈室炉烟<g ref="#CB23016"/>風
<lb ed="D" n="0781b09"/>起禪堂松<g ref="#CB28969"/>微隻履乍来留化跡五天何<g ref="#CB20060"/>又逢<g ref="#CB08221"/>解
<lb ed="D" n="0781b10"/>空弟子絕悲喜猶自<g ref="#CB15514"/>然對雪幃</l></lg></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
